#

High-Protein Veggie Power Sandwich

$6.5
450 kcal

Allergens:

GlutenSoy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianHigh-ProteinLow-Calorie

Tags:

SandwichVegetarianProtein-RichQuick Meal

Description

A hearty, protein-packed veggie sandwich bursting with flavor and nutrition.

Ingredients

  • Whole grain bread: 2 slices
  • Hummus: 3 tablespoons
  • Sliced avocado: 1/2
  • Sliced cucumber: 1/2
  • Sliced bell pepper: 1/2
  • Spinach leaves: 1 cup
  • Tofu (firm, sliced and grilled): 100 grams
  • Sprouts (alfalfa or mung bean): 1/4 cup
  • Lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
  • Salt and pepper: to taste
